     FGDKPL10 IF  E           K        DISK
     FQPRINT  O   F     198     OF     PRINTER
     E****************************************************************
     E                    MSG     1   2 59
     E                    PT      1   8  1   PTN    30
     E                    AM         12 11 0
     E                    AM2        12  9 0
     E                    AM3        12  9 0
